Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Anxiety over Soviet superpower
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b03z99j5
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 11 Apr 1976
Kissinger warns of risk to NATO from growing Soviet superpower. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.